{"tid":1722363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PornHub現多條fake news片, 抹黑香港示威","createTime":"2019-11-15T01:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T01:47:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"039bddc628c5c232ba73623249373b842fa23faa","tid":1722363,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:14:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191115/60269072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191115%2F60269072&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=061dee1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191115%2F60269072&h=fbb2eef4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191115/60269072</a><br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】PornHub現撐警片 五毛為抹黑抗爭無所不用其極<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1115 08:30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/frmqnd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffrmqnd7.jpg&h=bdc9d357&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n截至香港時間本周五，Pornhub上仍有香港一名男子被縱火「私了」及「抗爭天使」的影片。Pornhub(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n（北美通訊）繼Facebook、Twitter及YouTube後，全球最大色情影片網站PornHub也成為中國網民「翻牆」的目標，散播有關香港抗爭運動的假消息。更有美國傳媒發現自稱是「共青團中央」開設的頻道，上載多達11條影片，但目前已經消失。<br />\n<br />\n記者：林于鈴<br />\n<br />\n美國網媒《Quartz》發現，在微博有368萬粉絲的博主「孤煙暮蟬」本周二發文，表示「油管（YouTube）不讓傳視頻，逼的沒辦法，現在是全部傳到P站（Pornhub）去了」。<br />\n記者周三瀏覽Pornhub網站，搜尋「Hong Kong rioters」等字眼，便發現十多條支持香港警察、抹黑香港示威者為「暴徒」、「曱甴」、「港獨分子」、「分離主義者」的影片，亦包括早前香港一名男子被縱火「私了」、央視女主播李梓萌報道新聞、「抗爭天使」等片段。<br />\n報道指中國一向以「精神污染」為由，封殺總部位於加拿大的Pornhub，相信愛國網民透過翻牆來上傳影片。<br />\n<br />\n記者亦發現一條名叫「共青團中央」（CCYL_central）的頻道，於三個月前在Pornhub成立，並上傳了11條抹黑香港抗爭的影片，獲32人訂閱，9,000多次點擊。該頻道在自我介紹欄中表示興趣是「學習」，最喜愛的電視節目是「新聞聯播」，又說：「關注我，PH站也可以收穫正能量」。<br />\n<br />\n到周四，記者再找不到「共青團中央」的Pornhub頻道，但有關香港不實報道的影片依然存在。<br />\n報道指中國愛國網民自今年6月起，已透過外國社交媒體的假帳戶，抹黑香港抗爭運動，形容其手法笨拙（often quite clumsily），被Facebook、Twitter及YouTube封殺，刪除假帳戶。<br />\n今次並非色情影片首次介入香港「反送中」爭議。報道指出，很多已被刪除的Twitter假帳戶，在啓動抹黑行動前，經常轉載色情影片。今年6月，香港成年影片網站ThisAV亦號召網民上街，反對送中條例通過。"},{"pid":"f90b1fd0093b120fb038dd1a4e38b62c8882761f","tid":1722363,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:14:21.000Z","msg":"PornHub都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bbf4f8971bf1cf013d267acb3284ac306590e1","tid":1722363,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:15:48.000Z","msg":"又抄"},{"pid":"913490bb940171540e8348cef372f3bfb1835f18","tid":1722363,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:18:40.000Z","msg":"只可以講佢地太錯判形勢<br />\n到今日都仲妄想可以抹黑到我地絲毫"},{"pid":"dbd2936faa9d06643fe01084f0718126baf7f8dd","tid":1722363,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:20:50.000Z","msg":"只會畀外國人睇到佢地幾咁醜陋"},{"pid":"af9501b19d921e69d0b7e7957ad913590f544e83","tid":1722363,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:21:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人擺維尼同柒婆扑嘢片上去"},{"pid":"92e43437289ac794dacbd2bf41579998ad42937c","tid":1722363,"uid":241723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"913490bb940171540e8348cef372f3bfb1835f18","tid":1722363,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:18:40.000Z","msg":"只可以講佢地太錯判形勢<br />\n到今日都仲妄想可以抹黑到我地絲毫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:22:55.000Z","msg":"國際層面難講"},{"pid":"3065f71668a76705a39a8d110714196f1380049b","tid":1722363,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:24:57.000Z","msg":"塞鐵會比廢佬打<br />\n<br />\n佢打完你警察唔會拉，淨係拉你<br />\n<br />\n所以其實應該用火<br />\n<br />\n1份報紙，1枝火柴<br />\n<br />\n轉第二個站搞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b2c45c1a705cd01e6c6b2710aca1fe6a9a6ff6","tid":1722363,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b53d43a6e362f7e47429547f578f483b4176b2","tid":1722363,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ce22235674d28a75f80f5704b0ebc0c22d0171","tid":1722363,"uid":16844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:32:55.000Z","msg":"可以點做，report?"},{"pid":"f960172fd6719434bdb16eb8936e0a9106604515","tid":1722363,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}